Another debt and construction-based alternative, with huge gaps in the balance of payments, such as the one that has presided over Spanish growth in the boom years, will simply not tolerate it.
The invitation is clear.
And we'd be wrong not to understand it.
It is not just a matter of bringing the public deficit back to 3% in 2013.
What is required of us is much harder.
